high_descs: Turn left to face the red pillow on the couch.
Pick the paper up from the couch.
Turn around and face the table with the statue of a hand.
Put the paper on the table.
Go left and then turn right to face the green chair.
Pick the paper up from the chair.
Turn around and face the coffee table.
Put the paper down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two papers on a table.

high_descs: Move to the left side of the large green sofa
Pick up the newspaper on top of the sofa right of the red cushion
Carry the newspaper to the coffee table
Place the newspaper to the right of the hand statue on the coffee table
Move to the single green chair
Pick up the newspaper on top of the chair
Carry the newspaper to the coffee table
Place the newspaper to the left of the other newspaper on top of the table
anns.task_desc: Move two newspapers to the coffee table

high_descs: Turn left, go to the green couch, and turn left to face the red cushion on the green couch.
Take the newspaper from the green couch.
Turn left, go to the green chair, turn left, go to the fireplace, and turn left.
Put the newspaper on the white table.
Turn around, go to the wall, turn right, and go to the green chair.
Take the newspaper from the green chair.
Turn around, go to the brown shelf, turn left, and go to the white table.
Put the newspaper on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place two newspapers on the white coffee table.
